<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="assure-vt">assure <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'ʃʊə(r);ə'ʃɔː(r)/    美 /ə'ʃʊr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[多接从句] 向…保证：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>assure</strong> you <strong>that</strong> this medicine cannot harm you.
我向你保证这药对你没有害处。</p></div></div>